curl.title: curl 7.64
curl.description:
Runs all requests through libcurl with the following settings: 
SSL_VERIFYPEER=0, COOKIEJAR=./cookiejar.txt, COOKIESESSION=1, FOLLOWLOCATION=1, AUTOREFERER=1
